<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>267</hymn_number>
<title>FOR CHRISTAND THE CHURCH</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Krista Sapchuom di'n I ding,
 Lunggil a kizawm in;
 Muk a pak thu gen di'n,
 I khut hatlo huh di'n;
 I keng mangthai hawl di'n,
 Krista, Sapchuom di'n.

[V2]
 Krista Sapchuom di'n I ding,
 Lunggil a kizawm in;
 Tu apat I hinnau I pieu,
 Krista, Sapchuom di'n.

[V3]
 2. Krista Sapchuom di'n I ngen,
 Ni chenga sem zelin;
 Gunchuh leh hangsan in,
 Na chuh sem zel dingin;
 I thuthun tudet in,
 Krista, Sapchuom di'n.

[V4]
 3. Krista Sapchuom di'n la sa'n,
 Kipak a chawian in;
 Ei suohchak sak ziekin,
 Zawhna ei tiem ziekin;
 I thupiu hizing hen,
 Krista, Sapchuom di'n.</lyrics>
</song>